snippet.title: The Chant - Launch Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out what the international media are saying about The Chant. 

If you’re a horror fan you won’t want to miss this game. Enjoy its great atmosphere and its addictive, engaging and intriguing story. 

The Chant - developed by Brass Token and published by Prime Matter is out now on Xbox Series X/S, PS5 and PC.
 
Keep up to date with the latest news by following us on social: 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/TheChantGame 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheChantGame 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thechantgame 
Official Website: https://www.thechant.com

#TheChant #HorrorGame #PrimeMatter #horrorgaming
